snippet.title: Kamikaze Lassplanes | Steam Next Fest 2024 Teaser
snippet.description:
Ever thought of taking a plane on a date? Well, now you can! 🩷 Sort of... 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2253930/Kamikaze_Lassplanes/
Play the first chapter of Kamikaze Lassplanes for FREE as part of Steam Festival! We've got girls that turn into airplanes, romance, drama, branching choices and SHMUP gameplay sections ⸜(｡ ˃ ᵕ ˂ )⸝♡
